{"tid":2090978,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"官質疑17歲男生襲擊案休班警作假口供 律政司：會研究是否跟進","createTime":"2020-07-02T12:41:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-02T13:31:32.000Z","uid":240362,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f8ac09a72c157697235eed7f5e54217a73752d07","tid":2090978,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T12:41:45.000Z","msg":"休班男警去年7月30晚上，途徑天秀輕鐵站附近的行人隧道遭人群推撞，期間一名17歲男生徐瑋樂涉嫌開遮「篤」向休班警心口，他受審後在屯門法院獲裁定一項普通襲擊罪脫。葉啓亮裁判官判辭中指出，休班警口供矛盾，一共出現三個版本，辯方質疑休班警宣誓下作假口供，要求法庭轉介律政司處理。律政司發言人回覆指，會研究裁判官的判決理據和主控官的報告，然後決定是否需要跟進。<br />\n<br />\nSOURCE: 頭條"},{"pid":"3909b684cffdde03383d4dcbf9729ef6cea3a4ab","tid":2090978,"uid":151313,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T12:46:12.000Z","msg":"應該係跟進點樣炒咗個裁判官"},{"pid":"3a3876f7a3fba9c3b10ba1e4c10c13ae3e752b8e","tid":2090978,"uid":49669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3909b684cffdde03383d4dcbf9729ef6cea3a4ab","tid":2090978,"uid":151313,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T12:46:12.000Z","msg":"應該係跟進點樣炒咗個裁判官"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T12:57:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02b6c267725fbe92a63a174c82393a100cd3a003","tid":2090978,"uid":47311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T13:00:59.000Z","msg":"跟進用國安法入個學生<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a13944461c9d1ead4a3bee21136791a02e463027","tid":2090978,"uid":97398,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3909b684cffdde03383d4dcbf9729ef6cea3a4ab","tid":2090978,"uid":151313,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T12:46:12.000Z","msg":"應該係跟進點樣炒咗個裁判官"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T13:04:24.000Z","msg":"用國安法告鳩佢"},{"pid":"bf776c5555ae8d561d9fe6add82760d130f6cbdd","tid":2090978,"uid":168389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"202